snippet.title: Replay: Open Source Friday: Secure Code Game with Bartosz Gałek & jkcso
snippet.description: Join us for a special episode of Open Source Friday featuring Bartosz Gałek and jkcso, contributors to the Secure Code Game. Discover how Season 3 of Secure Code Game is empowering developers and students to build safer LLM-based applications, and get a look behind the scenes at the engineering decisions and open source journey.
